{"tid":88661,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"澳門節目：廣州話就等於「粵語方言」？","createTime":"2017-01-20T17:59:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-21T07:41:33.000Z","uid":53060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f2460a3806d152c8e1f187d05b7958e057e30f53","tid":88661,"uid":53060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T17:59:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">廣州話就等於粵語方言？</span>《趣智中文科》今集就會講下石岐話。三位歌手禤泳倫、古卓文、施朗明當中有兩位是土生人士，學習石岐話會否笑料百出？真的要靠來自利瑪竇中學三位學生軍師打救？有留意澳門文學的朋友，對寂然這個名字應該不陌生，今集他會介紹小說集《有發生過》，道出小城那些&ldquo;有發生過&rdquo;的事。敬請留意澳視澳門今晚九時三十分播映的《趣智中文科》。"},{"pid":"8ab688e7b12a446f27be9394a7aedc479547cd5e","tid":88661,"uid":53060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T17:59:50.000Z","msg":"[img]<a href=\"http://www.macaodaily.com/res/1/20170120/94261484847058515.jpg[/img]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.macaodaily.com%2Fres%2F1%2F20170120%2F94261484847058515.jpg%5B%2Fimg%5D&d=QEVk%2FwPgkJ%2FS4306LLtS%2FZkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=4108eef9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.macaodaily.com/res/1/20170120/94261484847058515.jpg[/img]</a><br />\n禤泳倫、古卓文、施朗明上《趣智中文科》。"},{"pid":"aeb6664221fc32ed70202993046eb8f35adf91be","tid":88661,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T19:51:21.000Z","msg":"方言都稱唔上，只係口音咋"},{"pid":"d4eb86bb6836f065b97835540045a663fdc0101c","tid":88661,"uid":27146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T20:08:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>方言都稱唔上，只係口音咋</blockquote><br />\n廣東話係口音咁西關音係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f759a10eef7664d694895ec0359df1437b0031c6","tid":88661,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T20:10:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>方言都稱唔上，只係口音咋</blockquote><br />\n廣東話係口音咁西關音係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/ass